# SEO Optimization Rules for Computer Recyclers USA Website

## Core SEO Principles

- Always prioritize user experience and valuable content over keyword stuffing
- Ensure all content is mobile-responsive and accessible
- Maintain consistent branding and messaging across all pages
- Focus on local SEO for Georgia and Southeast markets

## Page Structure & Metadata Requirements

### Required Metadata for Every Page

When creating or updating pages, ALWAYS include:

```typescript
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Specific Page Title | Computer Recyclers USA - [Location/Service]",
  description:
    "Compelling 150-160 character description with primary keywords and location",
  keywords:
    "Primary keyword, secondary keyword, location, service type, R2 certified",
  alternates: {
    canonical: "https://crusallc.com/[page-url]",
  },
  openGraph: {
    title: "Page Title for Social Sharing",
    description: "Social media optimized description",
    url: "https://crusallc.com/[page-url]",
    siteName: "Computer Recyclers USA",
    locale: "en_US",
    type: "website",
    images: [
      {
        url: "https://crusallc.com/logo.png",
        width: 1200,
        height: 630,
        alt: "Computer Recyclers USA - [Relevant Description]",
      },
    ],
  },
  twitter: {
    card: "summary_large_image",
    title: "Twitter Optimized Title",
    description: "Twitter optimized description",
    images: ["https://crusallc.com/logo.png"],
  },
  robots: {
    index: true,
    follow: true,
    googleBot: {
      index: true,
      follow: true,
      "max-video-preview": -1,
      "max-image-preview": "large",
      "max-snippet": -1,
    },
  },
};
```

### Title Tag Guidelines

- Keep titles under 60 characters
- Include primary keyword and location (Georgia/Southeast)
- Use pipe (|) separator before brand name
- Examples:
  - "Data Destruction Services Georgia | Computer Recyclers USA"
  - "IT Equipment Pickup Atlanta | Computer Recyclers USA"
  - "Electronics Recycling Suwanee GA | Computer Recyclers USA"

### Meta Description Guidelines

- Keep between 150-160 characters
- Include primary keyword and location
- Include a clear call-to-action
- Make it compelling and unique for each page
- Examples:
  - "Secure data destruction and electronics recycling in Georgia. R2 certified, free pickup, HIPAA compliant. Serving Atlanta, Savannah, Augusta & all of Georgia."
  - "Professional IT equipment pickup and responsible recycling in Georgia. Free statewide service, certified data destruction, EPA compliant processes."

## Content Optimization Rules

### Heading Structure (H1-H6)

- Use only ONE H1 per page (main page title)
- H2s for major sections, H3s for subsections
- Include target keywords naturally in headings
- Maintain logical hierarchy (H1 → H2 → H3)

### Keyword Integration

- Primary keywords: "data destruction", "electronics recycling", "computer recycling", "IT equipment pickup"
- Location keywords: "Georgia", "Atlanta", "Southeast", "Suwanee", "R2 certified"
- Service keywords: "secure data destruction", "responsible recycling", "free pickup"
- Include keywords naturally in:
  - First 100 words of content
  - Headings (H1, H2, H3)
  - Image alt text
  - Internal links

### Content Quality Standards

- Minimum 300 words per page
- Use bullet points and numbered lists for readability
- Include local business information (address, phone, hours)
- Add customer testimonials and certifications
- Include clear calls-to-action (CTAs)

## Technical SEO Requirements

### Image Optimization

- All images MUST have descriptive alt text
- Use Next.js Image component for optimization
- Include relevant keywords in alt text
- Examples:
  - "Mobile shredding unit for onsite data destruction in Georgia"
  - "Professional IT equipment pickup truck serving Atlanta area"
  - "R2 certified electronics recycling facility in Suwanee GA"

### Internal Linking

- Link to relevant service pages from main content
- Use descriptive anchor text with keywords
- Include links to contact page and pickup form
- Examples:
  - "Learn more about our [data destruction services]"
  - "Schedule your [free IT equipment pickup] today"

### URL Structure

- Use descriptive, keyword-rich URLs
- Keep URLs short and readable
- Use hyphens to separate words
- Examples:
  - `/services/data-destruction-georgia`
  - `/about/computer-recyclers-usa-atlanta`
  - `/contact/schedule-pickup-georgia`

## Local SEO Optimization

### Location-Based Content

- Always mention "Georgia" and "Southeast" in content
- Include specific cities: Atlanta, Savannah, Augusta, Columbus, Macon, Suwanee
- Reference local landmarks and business districts
- Include service area information

### Business Information Consistency

- Always use: "Computer Recyclers USA" (full name)
- Address: "3644 Burnette Road, Suwanee, GA 30024"
- Phone: "770-840-0805"
- Email: "info@crusallc.com"
