## Common SEO Mistakes to Avoid

- Don't stuff keywords unnaturally
- Don't duplicate content across pages
- Don't use generic or vague alt text
- Don't forget to include location keywords
- Don't create pages without clear purpose
- Don't ignore mobile optimization
- Don't skip structured data markup
- Don't use duplicate title tags
- Don't forget to update sitemap for new pages
- Don't ignore page loading speeds

